# Normalize line endings: store everything as LF in the repo.
# This project originated on Linux (Replit) and contains shell scripts;
# forcing LF prevents CRLF corruption when working on Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Shell scripts must stay LF or they break when executed on Linux.
*.sh text eol=lf

# Lockfiles/generated - treat as text but never show in diffs by default.
pnpm-lock.yaml -diff
